snippet.title: Hot Wheels Unleashed™ - Monster Trucks Expansion
snippet.description: Take the races to a literally EXTRA LARGE dimension! Everything is oversized in this expansion: wheels, vehicles, jumps and also the fun! A new themed environment, customisations and vehicles to have fun in a big way!
